hadiths[31]{hadithnumber,text}:
1493,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Qurbani key din Allah key nazdik aadmi ka sab sey mehbub amal khoon bahana hai, qiyamat key din qurbani key janwer apni seengon , baalon aur khuron key sath ayengey qurbani ka khoon zamin par girney sey pehley qubuliyat ka darja hasil kar leta hai, isliye khushdili key sath qurbani karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, Hisham bin Urwa ki is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Imran bin Husain aur Zaid bin Arqam Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- Raavi Abu Musanna ka naam Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yazeed hai, in sey ibne-Abi Fidya ney riwayat ki hai. 4- Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney farmaya : qurbani karney waley ko qurbani key janwer key har baal key badley neki mileygi.'' 5- ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke janwer ki seeng key iwaz neki mileygi."
1494,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney seeng waley do chitkabrey mendhon ki qurbani ki, aap ney un dono ko apney haath sey zibeh kiya, Bismillah padhi aur Allahu-Akbar kaha aur (zibeh kartey waqt) apna paaon unkey pahluon par rakha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Aaisha , Abu-Hurera , abu-Ayyub , Jabir , Abu-Darda , abu-Raafey , ibne-Umar aur abu-Bakra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1495,"wo do mendhon ki qurbani kartey they, eik Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki taraf sey aur doosra apni taraf sey , to un sey is barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney bataya ke mujhey iska hukm Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney diya hai, lihaza main isko kabhi nahin chhodunga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum is ko sirf Shareek ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Ali bin Madini ney kaha : is hadees ko Shareek key ilawa logon ney bhi riwayat kiya hai, mainey un sey daryaft kiya : Raavi Abul Hasna ka kya naam hai? to wo usey nahin jaan sakey , Muslim kehtey hain : uska naam Hasan hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney maiyat ki taraf sey qurbani ki rukhsat di hai aur baaz log maiyat ki taraf sey qurbani durust nahin samajhtey hain, Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : mujhey ye chiz ziyada pasand hai ke maiyat ki taraf sey sadqa kar diya jaey, qurbani na ki jaey, aur agar kisi ney uski taraf sey qurbani kar di to is mein sey kuchh na khaye balke tamam ko sadqa kar dey."
1496,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney seeng waley eik nar mendhey ki qurbani ki, wo siyahi mein khaata tha, siyahi mein chalta tha aur siyahi mein dekhta tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- hum isko sirf Hafs bin Ghiyas hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1497,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aisay langdey janwer ki qurbani na ki jaey jis ka langdapan wazeh (zahir) ho, na aisey andhey janwer ki jiska andhapan wazeh ho, na aisey bimar janwer ki jiski bimari wazeh ho, aur na aisey laaghir aur kamzor janwer ki qurbani ki jaey jiski haddi mein goodaa na ho.'' is sanad sey bhi Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey usi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, isey hum sirf Ubaid bin Feeroz ki hadees sey jantey hain unhoney Bara sey riwayat ki hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1498,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein hukm diya ke (qurbani waley janwer ki) aankh aur kaan achvhhi tarah dekh lein , aur aisey janwer ki qurbani na karen jiska kaan aagey sey kataa ho, ya jis ka kaan peechhey sey kataa ho, ya jis ka kaan cheera huwa ho (yani lambaai mein kataa huwa ho), ya jis key kaan mein surakh ho. is sanad sey bhi Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai, is mein ye izafa hai ke « مقابلة » wo janwer hai jis key kaan ka kinara ( aagey sey) kataa ho, « مدابرة » wo janwer hai jis key kaan ka kinara ( peechhey sey) kataa ho, « شرقاء » jis ka kaan ( lambaai mein) cheera huwa ho, aur « خرقاء » jis key kaan mein) gol ( surakh ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shureh bin Noman Saadi , Koofa key rehney waley hain aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key sathiyon mein sey hain. 3- Shureh bin Haani koofa key rehney waley hain aur unkey walid ko sharfe-sohbat hasil hai aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key sathi hain, aur Shureh bin Haris Kandi Abu Umayya Qazi hain, unhoney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, ye teeno Shureh (jinki tafsil ooper guzri) Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key sathi aur hum Asr hain. 4- « نستشرف » sey murad « ننظر صحيحا » hai yani qurbani key janwer ko hum achchhi tarah dekh lein."
1499,"Main Madina mein tijarat key liye jazaa yani dunbe key chhotey bachchey laya aur bazar manda ho gaya, lihaza mainey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey mulaqat ki, aur un sey puchha to unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''bhaid key bachchey ki qurbani khub hai !'' Abu Kibaash kehtey hain (ye suntey hi) log uski kharidari par toot padey. is baab mein ibne-Abbas , Umme Bilal binte Hilal ki unkey walid sey aur Jabir , Aqba bin Aamir Raziallahu anhum aur eik aadmi jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey hain sey bhi ahadees aai hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey moqufan bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- Usman bin Vaqdiya ibne Muhammad bin Ziyad bin Abdullah bin umr bin Khattab hain. 4- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai ke bhaid ka bachcha qurbani key liye kifaayat kar jaeyga."
1500,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen bakriyan den taake wo qurbani key liye Sahaba kiram key darmiyan taqseem kar den , eik « عتود » ( bakri ka eik saal ka farba bachcha (ya « جدي  baqi bach gaya, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey iska tazkira kiya, to aap ney farmaya : ''tum iski qurbani khud kar lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Wakee kehtey hain : bhed ka bachcha, chhe ya saat maah ka bachcha hota hai. 3- Aqba bin Aamir sey dusri sanad sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qurbani key janwer taqseem kiye , eik achcha baqi bach gaya, mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' tum iski qurbani khud kar lo.''"
1501,"Hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik safar mein they ke qurbani ka din aa gaya, chunanche hamney gaey ki qurbani mein saat aadmiyon aur oont ki qurbani mein das aadmiyon ko shareek kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Fazal bin Musa ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein (ابوالأ سد سلمی an أبیہ an جدہ) aur abu-Ayyub sey hadeesen aai hain."
1502,"Hum logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath hudaibiya key moqe par oont aur gaaey ko saat aadmiyon ki taraf sey nahar ( zibeh ( kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm aur unkey ilawa logon ka isi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. 3- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : oont das aadmi ki taraf sey bhi kifaayat kar jaeyga, unhoney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees sey daleel di hai."
1503,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : gaaey ki qurbani saat aadmiyon ki taraf sey ki jaeygi, Hujaiya kehtey hain : mainey puchha : agar wo bachcha janey? unhoney kaha : isi key sath usko bhi zibeh kar do, mainey kaha agar wo langdi ho? unhoney kaha : jab qurban-gaah tak pahunch jaey to isey zibeh kar do, mainey kaha : agar uskey seeng tootey hon? unhoney kaha : koi harj nahin, hamein hukm diya gaya hai, ya hamein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm diya hai ke hum unki aakhon aur kanon ko khub dekh bhaal lein. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees ko Sufiyan ney Salma bin Kuheil sey riwayat kiya hai."
1504,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un janweron ki qurbani karney sey mana farmaya jin key seeng tootey aur kaan phatey huye hon. Qatada kehtey hain : mainey Saeed bin Musaiyab sey iska tazkira kiya to unhoney kaha : « عضب » ( seeng tootney ( sey murad ye hai ke seeng aadhi ya is sey ziyada tooti ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1505,"Mainey Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein qurbaaniyaan kaisey hoti thi? unhoney kaha : eik aadmi apni aur apney ghar walon ki taraf sey eik bakri qurbani karta tha, wo log khud khatey they aur dusron ko khilatey they yahan tak ke log ( kasrate-qurbani par) fakhr karney lagey, aur ab ye soorate-haal ho gaee jo dekh rahey ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Raavi Imaara bin Abdullah Madni hain, insey Malik bin Anas ney bhi riwayat ki hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai, un dono ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki is hadees sey daleel di hai ke aap ney eik mendhey ki qurbani ki aur farmaya : ''ye meri ummat key un logon ki taraf sey hai, jinhoney qurbani nahin ki hai.'' 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : eik bakri eik hi aadmi ki taraf sey kifaayat kareygi, Abdullah bin Mubarak aur doosrey ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai (lekin raajeh (behtar) pehla qol hai)."
1506,"Eik aadmi ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey qurbani key barey mein puchha : kya ye wajib hai? to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aur musalmanon ney qurbani ki hai, us aadmi ney phir apna sawal dohraya , unhoney kaha : samajhtey nahin ho? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aur musalmanon ney qurbani ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke qurbani wajib nahin hai, balke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki sunnaton mein sey eik sunnat hai, aur is par amal karna mustahab hai, Sufiyan Sory aur ibne-Mubarak ka yehi qol hai."
1507,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Madina mein das saal muqeem rahey aur aap (har saal ( qurbani kartey rahey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
1508,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qurbani key din hamein khutba diya, aap ney khutbe key doran farmaya : ''jab tak namaze-Eid ada na kar ley koi hergiz qurbani na karey.'' Bara kehtey hain : merey mamu khadey huye padhi. , aur unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! ye aisa din hai jis mein) ziyada honey ki wajeh sey) gosht qabile-nafrat ho jata hai, isliye mainey apni qurbani jald kar di taake apney baal bachchon aur ghar walon ya padausiyon ko khila sakoon? aap ney farmaya : ''phir dusri qurbani karo.''  unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! merey paas doodh peeti pathiya hai aur gosht wali do bakriyon sey behtar hai, kya main us ko zibeh kar dun? aap ney farmaya : ''haan ! wo tumhari dono qurbaaniyon sey behtar hai, lekin tumharey baad kisi key liye Juzaa ( bachchey ( ki qurbani kafi na hogi.'' is baab mein Jabir , Jundub , Anas , Uwemir bin Ashkar, ibne-Umar aur abu-Zaid Ansari Raziallahu anhum sey bhi ahadees aai hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke jab tak Imam namaze-Eid na ada kar ley shehar mein qurbani na ki jaey. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney jab Fajr tulu ho jaey to gaanoon walon key liye qurbani ki rukhsat (choot) di hai, ibne-Mubarak ka bhi yehi qol hai. 4- ehle-ilm ka ijmaa' (aam sahmati) hai ke bakri key جذع (chhe maah key bachchey) ki qurbani durust nahin hai, wo kehtey hain albatta bheed key bachche ki qurbani durust hai."
1509,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi teen din sey ziyada qurbani ka gosht na khaye.''  is baab mein Aaisha aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki taraf sey ye mumaaniat pehley thi, uskey baad aap ney ijazat dey di."
1510,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney tum logon ko teen din sey ziyada qurbani ka gosht rakhney sey mana kiya tha taake maaldaar log un logon key liye kushadgi kar den jinhen qurbani ki taqat nahin hai, so ab jitna chaho khud khaao dusron ko khilaao aur) gosht ( jama kar key rakho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Barida ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Aaisha , Nabeesha , abu-Saeed , Qatada bin Noman , Anas aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1511,"Mainey Ummul-momenin sey kaha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam qurbani ka gosht rakhney sey mana farmatey they? wo bolin : nahin, lekin us waqt bahut kam log qurbani kartey they, isliye aap chahtey they ke jo log qurbani nahin kar sakey hain unhen khilaya jaey, hum log qurbani key janwer key paey rakh detey phir in ko das din baad khatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, Ummul-momenin (jin sey hadees mazkur marvi hai) wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki biwi Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) hain, in sey ye hadees kaee sanadon sey aai hai."
1512,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(Islam mein) na (faraa) hai na (ateera)‏ (faraa) janwer ka wo pehla bachcha hai jo kafiron key yahan paida hota to wo usey ( buton key naam par) zibeh kar detey they.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Nabeesha, Mikhnaf bin Sulem aur Abu Ushara sey bhi ahadees aai hain,  Abu Ushara apney walid sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- (ateera) wo zabiha hai jisey ehale-Makka rajab key mahine mein us maah ki tazeem key liye zibeh kartey they isliye ke hurmat key mahinon mein rajab pehla mahina hai, aur hurmat key mahiney rajab, zi-qaada, zii-hijja, aur muhrram hain, aur Haj key mahiney shawwaal, zi-qaada aur zil-hijja key (ibtidaai) das din hain. Haj key mahinon key silsiley mein baaz Sahaba aur doosrey logon sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1513,"Log Hafsa binte Abdur-Rehman key paas gaey aur un sey Aqeeqe key barey mein puchha to unhoney bayan kiya ke (unki phuphi) Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney in ko bataya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Sahaba ko hukm diya ke wo ladkey ki taraf sey do bakriyan eik jaisi aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri Aqeeqa karen. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Hafsa , Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti hain. 2- is bab mein Ali , Umme Kurz, Barida , Samura, Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr , Anas , Salman bin Aamir aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1514,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke Hasan bin Ali jab Fatima zohra (Raziallauh anhum) sey paida huye to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hasan key kaan mein namaz ki Azan ki tarah Azan di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Aqeeqa key masle mein is hadees par amal hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaee sanadon sey aai hai ke ladkey ki taraf sey do bakriyan eik jaisi aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri zibeh ki jaey. 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney Hasan ki taraf sey eik bakri zibeh ki, baaz ehle-ilm ka maslak isi hadees key muwaafiq hai."
1515,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ladkey ki paidaish par Aqeeqa lazim hai, lihaza uski taraf sey khoon bhaao (janwer zibeh karo) aur us sey gandagi door karo.'' is sanad sey bhi Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1516,"Unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Aqeeqa key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''ladkey ki taraf sey do bakriyan aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri zibeh ki jaeygi, wo janwer nar ya ho mada is main tumharey liye koi harj nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1517,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qurbani key janweron mein sab sey behtar mendhaa hai aur sab sey behtar kafan « حلة » ( tehband aur chadar ( hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Afeer bin Maadaan hadees ki riwayat mein zaeef hain.
1518,"Hum log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath maidan Arafat mein thehrey huye they, mainey aap ko farmatey suna : logo ! har ghar waley par har saal eik qurbani aur « عتيرة » (ateera) hai, tum log jantey ho « عتيرة » (ateera) kya hai? « عتيرة » (ateera) wo hai jisey tum log (rajbiya) kehtey ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum is ko ibne Aun hi ki sanad sey jantey hain."
1519,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hasan ki taraf sey eik bakri aqeeqa kiya, aur farmaya : ''Faatima ! iska sar moond do aur iskey baal key barabar chaandi sadqa karo.''  Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) ney uskey baal ko tola to uska wazan eik dirham key barabar ya us sey kuchh kam huwa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- iski sanad muttasil nahin hai, aur Raavi Abu-Jafar Sadiq Muhammad bin Ali bin Husain ney Ali bin abi Talib ko nahin paya hai."
1520,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khutba diya, phir ( member sey) utrey phir aap ney do mendhey mangaaey aur in ko zibeh kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. (ye Eidul-Azha ki namaz key baad kiya tha, dekhey agli hadees)."
1521,"Main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Eidul-Azha key din Eid-gaah gaya, jab aap khutba khatam kar chukey to member sey nichey utrey, phir eik mendhaa laya gaya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us ko apney haath sey zibeh kiya, aur (zibeh kartey waqt) ye kalimaat kahey : (بسم الله والله أكبر ، هذا عني وعمن لم يضح من أمتي). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- ehle-ilm Sahaba aur deegar logon ka isi par amal hai ke janwer zibeh kartey waqt aadmi ye kahey « بسم الله والله أكبر » ibne-Mubarak ka bhi yehi qol hai, kaha jata hai. 3- Raavi Muttalib bin Abdullah bin Hantab ka samaa (sun'na), Jabir sey sabit nahin hai."
1522,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har bacha Aqeeqe key badley girwi rakha huwa hai padhi. , paidaish key saatwen din uska Aqeeqa kiya jaey, uska naam rakha jaey aur uskey sar key baal mundaaey jaeyn.''"
1523,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo maah zil-hijj ka chaand dekhey aur qurbani karna chahta ho wo ( jab tak qurbani na kar ley ( apna baal aur nakhun na kaatey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- (Amr aur umr key barey mein) sahih Amr bin Muslim hai, in sey Muhammad bin Amr bin Alqama aur kaee logon ney hadees riwayat ki hai, dusri sanad sey isi jaisi hadees Saeed bin Musaiyab sey aai hai, Saeed bin Musaiyab abu-Salma sey aur abu-Salma Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, Saeed bin Musaiyab bhi isi key qaail hain, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka maslak bhi isi hadees key muwaafiq hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney is silsiley mein rukhsat di hai, wo log kehtey hain : baal aur nakhun kaatney mein koi harj nahin hai, Shafai ka yehi qol hai, wo Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki is hadees sey daleel detey hain, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam qurbani ka janwer Madina rawana kartey they aur mohrim jin chizon sey ijtinab (bacha) karta hai, aap un mein sey kisi chiz sey bhi ijtinab (bacha) nahin kartey they."
